** Data Quality Challenges
***[#white] ====<size:14>Data Entry Errors
****[#yellow] ====<size:14>Mistakes made during data input.
***[#white] ====<size:14>Data Duplication
****[#yellow] ====<size:14>Repeated data entries that lead to inconsistency.
***[#white] ====<size:14>Incomplete Data
****[#yellow] ====<size:14>Missing values or records in datasets.
***[#white] ====<size:14>Inconsistent Formats
****[#yellow] ====<size:14>Data stored in various formats or units.
***[#white] ====<size:14>Data Decay
****[#yellow] ====<size:14>Data becoming outdated over time.
***[#white] ====<size:14>Data Silos
****[#yellow] ====<size:14>Data isolated in different parts of an organization.
***[#white] ====<size:14>Lack of Data Governance
****[#yellow] ====<size:14>Absence of data quality management policies.

